snippet.title: Offensive Combat: Redux! - Fly Through - Slums
snippet.description: Here's the first of a series of fly through videos highlighting the different maps in Offensive Combat: Redux! We're currently in beta - if you want to try the game and are in North America or Europe, email beta@ocredux.com for a beta key. http://store.steampowered.com/app/622170/Offensive_Combat_Redux/
